  "comment": {
    "text": "This key provides a confirmation message displayed in a dialog when disabling the Backup service. It explains the consequences of disabling backups, including the impact on administrators and the status of Auto Backup, and asks the user to confirm their decision. The message includes a variable for the product name.",
